    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/98d718ce0429ce065f880d0bd19c61c5.poster.avif?t=1739609753\" width=700 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/98d718ce0429ce065f880d0bd19c61c5.webm?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/98d718ce0429ce065f880d0bd19c61c5.mp4?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你可以免费玩一款精美打磨、充满动作的游戏——没有微交易，没有广告，只有纯粹的乐趣，那会怎么样？这正是我们提供的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是两位独立开发者，想要用不同的方式推广游戏。与其向你介绍我们的付费游戏 Rocket Boots Mania，我们更希望你能通过这款完全免费的独立游戏，亲身体验它的高速世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是一个试玩版——而是完整的、无任何限制的体验，包含数小时精心打磨的游戏内容。立即加入，探索并感受 Rocket Boots Mania 的精彩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/fb20cd2d1e90f8eea12241f60affa9f9.poster.avif?t=1739609753\" width=700 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/fb20cd2d1e90f8eea12241f60affa9f9.webm?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/fb20cd2d1e90f8eea12241f60affa9f9.mp4?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入 ROCKETEX，一家提供火箭靴的快递公司！使用火箭跳跃、滑行、墙跑、翻转和飞行，在疾驰的太空列车上营救丢失的货物，穿越整个银河系！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/b2ae2a12940c76b250cc5bbda4241c74.poster.avif?t=1739609753\" width=700 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/b2ae2a12940c76b250cc5bbda4241c74.webm?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/b2ae2a12940c76b250cc5bbda4241c74.mp4?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是普通的跑酷游戏。在这款游戏中，你掌控一切！自由移动，极速穿越迷人的银河风景。随心所欲地探索——竞速冲刺，或者放松身心，欣赏周围的宁静氛围。这是一款拥有全新自由度的无限跑酷游戏！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/aaedede83ed4c2d494696b9c901e171e.poster.avif?t=1739609753\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/aaedede83ed4c2d494696b9c901e171e.webm?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318940/extras/aaedede83ed4c2d494696b9c901e171e.mp4?t=1739609753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别担心，ROCKETEX 为所有技能水平的玩家提供了任务——初学者、普通和专家模式！每个模式都有独特的任务和专属统计追踪器，帮助你查看进度和提升表现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，你还在等什么？ROCKETEX 需要你的帮助！<br><br><strong>立即将游戏加入愿望单 🏃‍♂️🔥</strong></p>",
